9.6.19  12:53 am   can you give us a TINY hint on your next project?

      one of my main pieces of video software was discontinued in 2011. i didn't even start using it until 2013. i didn't find out it was discontinued until about 2016, when i had already had 3 years of experience using it. there was never a good time to re-learn everything i know, so i kicked the can down the road and continued using it until 2019, still continuing to get better and learn more and more tricks on it. then i got hooked on 3d anyway, so i figured it was a good time to start making the transition, but the transition has turned out to be much more vast and exciting than i ever could have imagined. currently in the midst of drastically re-imagining everything i do. it should only take a few more minutes
